Taking into consideration that on November 20, 1962 the Government of the United
                    States suspended the quarantine it introduced on October 23, 1962 regarding the
                    ships bound for the Republic of Cuba;

Taking further into consideration the statement of the United States Government
                    as contained in its declaration of (blank) 1962 to the effect that the United
                    States will not invade Cuba or support an invasion of Cuba;
